No. 11-6195. Mark Anthony Evans, aka Mark Evans, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 960, 132 S. Ct. 433,

181 L. Ed. 2d 288,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7158. October 11, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
